I have deployed an application in guvi.com:9000, and logs shows my app is running, but Iâ€™m unable to view the page. Check whether my port is open or not ?
by using command :sudo lsof -i :9000
If the result is empty (returns no output), the port is not open. Otherwise, it will show the process associated with port 9000.
